            <p>ΕΝΤΩΚΑΛΩΤΟΠ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><lb/>
ΜΝΕΙϹΘΗΗΛΙΑϹΚsϹΕ<unclear>Β</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><lb/>
               <unclear>ΟΜ</unclear>ΑΡΙΑ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ΒΟϹϹΤΡ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/>ΗϹ<lb/>
               ΜΕΤΑΤΩΝΑΓΑΠΟΝΤΩΝΑΥΤΟ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/>
            </p>
